title: #92Noon! 10am Hour 12/22 - Guerin/Albert/Boudreau
description: Wild head coach Bill Guerin calls in to talk about USA hockey players withdrawing from the Olympics, play-by-play commentator Kenny Albert joins the show to break down the Winter Classic, plus a conversation with former Wild head coach Bruce Boudreau.
